    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在一间神秘的公共公寓中，周围充满了奇怪而令人不安的气氛。这里似乎没有出路，你唯一的选择是一部有两个按钮的旧电梯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走过走廊，当你注意到异常情况——某些不该出现的东西时，按下电梯的<strong>红色按钮</strong>。如果一切看起来正常，则按下<strong>绿色按钮</strong>。你的选择将决定结局：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正确的选择会让你更接近出口。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >错误的选择会将你送回起点。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与观察：</strong> 仔细检查走廊和周围环境。异常现象可能隐藏在走廊的任何地方。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>决策能力：</strong> 测试你的注意力和直觉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可重复性：</strong> 每次游戏都会为你带来新的异常和挑战组合。游戏包含大约30种独特异常，在一个循环中不会重复。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逼真的画面：</strong> 精美的视觉效果营造出身临其境且令人毛骨悚然的氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实的氛围：</strong> 感受充满秘密的老式公共公寓的独特气息。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现奇怪甚至有些滑稽的异常现象：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态异常：</strong> 等待你的是一系列怪异、搞笑却又令人不寒而栗的现象。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一锅里的头并不是你可能遇到的最恐怖的事情：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可爱的猫咪：</strong> 这位毛茸茸的伙伴可能比看起来更加神秘。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你能逃出去吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是会被困在一个错误决定的无尽循环中？一切都取决于你的观察力和直觉。</p>",
